title: OXO TOT Breast Pump Parts Drying Rack
description: This compact Drying Rack features two cleaning brushes specifically designed for breast pump parts that store compactly inside and stand up automatically when the Rack is opened. The loop brush is perfect for breast shields, valves and connectors, while the detail brush is great for threads and other intricate spaces. The elevated ridges keep parts elevated above water for quick drying.

transcripts: Busy moms on the go may find themselves needing to clean their breast pump parts while not at home. Our drying rack with detail brushes is the perfect compact solution. This compact drying rack features 2 cleaning brushes specifically designed fro breast pump parts. The brushes store compactly inside ans stand up automatically when the rack is open. The loop brush is perfect for breast shields, valves and connectors, while the detail brush is great for threads and other intricate spaces. When open the drying rack is ideal for drying parts the raised ridges keep the breast pump parts elevated above standing water for quick drying. The rack folds discretely for compact storage in travel, diaper, and breast pump bags. Here's a good tip, rinse your breast pump parts with cool water before using hot soapy water to prevent sticky residue.
